{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"7914","heading":"Availability of counter-cyclical payments","label":"7914 Availability of counter-cyclical payments","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/ch106/schI","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7914","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextSubchapter II, referred to in subsec. (b)(1)(B), was in the original “subtitle B”, meaning subtitle B (§§ 1201–1209) of title I of , , , which is classified principally to subchapter II of this chapter. For complete classification of subtitle B to the Code, see Tables.Pub. L. 107–171116 Stat. 155May 13, 2002"],"amendments":["References in TextSubchapter II, referred to in subsec. (b)(1)(B), was in the original “subtitle B”, meaning subtitle B (§§ 1201–1209) of title I of , , , which is classified principally to subchapter II of this chapter. For complete classification of subtitle B to the Code, see Tables.Pub. L. 107–171116 Stat. 155May 13, 2002"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Payment required","label":"a Payment required","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7914%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For each of the 2002 through 2007 crop years for each covered commodity, the Secretary shall make counter-cyclical payments to producers on farms for which payment yields and base acres are established with respect to the covered commodity if the Secretary determines that the effective price for the covered commodity is less than the target price for the covered commodity.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Effective price","label":"b Effective price","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7914%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7914%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/b/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7914%2Fb%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The national average market price received by producers during the 12-month marketing year for the covered commodity, as determined by the Secretary.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/b/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7914%2Fb%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The national average loan rate for a marketing assistance loan for the covered commodity in effect for the applicable period under subchapter II.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7914%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The payment rate in effect for the covered commodity under for the purpose of making direct payments with respect to the covered commodity.section 7913 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Target price","label":"c Target price","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7914%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"2002 and 2003 crop years","label":"1 2002 and 2003 crop years","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7914%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/c/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7914%2Fc%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Wheat, $3.86 per bushel.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/c/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7914%2Fc%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Corn, $2.60 per bushel.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/c/1/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7914/c/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7914%2Fc%2F1%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Grain sorghum, $2.54 per bushel.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"childr